      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable daily driver that's ready to get to work? This car has been a dependable companion and is perfect for someone who values functionality and a solid engine over a flawless exterior. It shows some honest wear and tear from its years on the road, but it still runs strong and offers a great, budget-friendly way to get where you need to go!",
