      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a functional daily driver for someone willing to put in a little TLC. While the engine and transmission are operational, you will notice some cosmetic issues including visible paint fading on the roof and a few minor dents along the rear bumper. The interior shows significant wear on the upholstery and the air conditioning is not as cold as it used to be. It remains a dependable car for getting from A to B, but it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future.",
